<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>54 square units. Sample response: I split the figure into 2 rectangles, 1 across the top and 1 below. I found the area of the rectangle across the top by multiplying <m>3 \times 10</m>, which is 30. I found the area of the bottom rectangle by multiplying <m>4 \times 6</m>, which is 24. Then, I added the area of both rectangles to get 54.</p>
